  "title": "DRIVER",
  "description": "<p>Job Description</p><p>Drive Class 4 vehicles (e.g. 24-ft lorries, box trucks, trailers) for local freight transportation</p><p>Perform delivery and collection of goods according to daily schedules</p><p>Ensure goods are properly handled and safely transported</p><p>Assist in loading and unloading of cargo when required</p><p>Conduct daily vehicle checks and ensure the vehicle is well maintained and kept clean</p><p>Comply with Singapore traffic regulations and company operational procedures</p><p>Complete delivery orders, transport records and related documentation</p><p>Carry out any other duties as assigned by the supervisor</p><p></p><p>Job Requirements</p><p>Possess a valid Singapore Class 4 driving licence</p><p>Minimum 3 years of relevant experience (logistics or transport industry preferred)</p><p>Familiar with Singapore road network and traffic regulations</p><p>Physically fit and able to perform long hours of driving and manual work</p><p>Responsible, reliable, and punctual with a good working attitude</p><p>Able to work independently and as part of a team</p><p>Willing to work overtime or on shift when required</p>",
